parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Software-related issues can cause unexpected behavior, safety risks, and inconvenience to the driver.
symptoms: Vehicle goes into neutral or park unexpectedly
warning lights and messages appear on the dashboard
loss of connectivity and functionality of safety features
and sunroof explosion.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Connectivity and technology issues can cause inconvenience, distraction, and safety risks to the driver.
symptoms: Loss of connectivity and functionality of safety features
poor software design
and distracting user interface.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive tire wear can cause safety risks, especially when driving at high speeds.
symptoms: Excessive tire wear
cupping of tires
and noise from tires.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical and mirror issues can cause safety risks and inconvenience to the driver.
symptoms: Mirrors adjust unexpectedly
and electric connectors malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Powertrain Malfunction and Sudden Loss of Power
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden loss of power can cause accidents, especially when driving at high speeds, and leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
the "Powertrain Malfunction" warning light displays on the dashboard
the vehicle stalls or hesitates to accelerate
the electric engine or gasoline engine fails to respond.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents, and result in costly repairs.
symptoms: The transmission fluid level is higher than normal
the electric drive buffer spring wears a hole in the transmission casing
the vehicle hesitates to accelerate or stalls.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Hybrid Battery Failure and Warranty Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hybrid battery can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents, and result in costly repairs.
symptoms: The hybrid battery fails
the vehicle displays "Powertrain Malfunction" warning light
the vehicle loses power
the battery is not properly charged.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electrical System Failure and Wiring Harness Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents, and result in costly repairs.
symptoms: The electrical machine electronics (EME) wiring harness connector fails
the vehicle displays "Powertrain Malfunction" warning light
the vehicle loses power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic A/C compressor can cause the high voltage battery system to overheat, risking a fire, and prevent the vehicle from charging or using the high voltage batteries.
symptoms: The A/C system fails to cool the cabin and high voltage battery packs
and the vehicle cannot charge or use the high voltage batteries.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The false illumination of the service repair light can lead to a lack of awareness of actual issues with the vehicle, potentially causing safety risks and unexpected breakdowns.
symptoms: The service repair light is illuminated
but no issue is shown when checked; inability to receive alerts on the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water leaking into the electrical system can cause damage to the vehicle's electrical components, leading to safety risks and unexpected breakdowns.
symptoms: Water leaking into the dashboard and electrical system; dealers misdiagnosing the issue as a clogged drain tube.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the auxiliary cooling fan can cause engine overheating, leading to engine damage and potential safety risks.
symptoms: Engine overheating; no engine light illumination.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Damage to the EME board can cause the vehicle to become unstable, leading to safety risks and unexpected breakdowns.
symptoms: Failure to start the vehicle; EME board damage after jump-starting the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to safety risks and unexpected breakdowns.
symptoms: Vehicle stalling while driving; no warning lights or indicators prior to stalling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the dashboard can cause a lack of awareness of important vehicle information, potentially leading to safety risks and unexpected breakdowns.
symptoms: Dashboard becoming blank while driving; issue disappears after restarting the engine.
